&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Figma is growing our team of passionate creatives and builders on a mission to make design accessible to all. Figma’s platform helps teams bring ideas to life—whether you&#39;re brainstorming, creating a prototype, translating designs into code, or iterating with AI. From idea to product, Figma empowers teams to streamline workflows, move faster, and work together in real time from anywhere in the world. If you&#39;re excited to shape the future of design and collaboration, join us!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Core to Figma’s success—and heart—is our community. As we scale into new geographies and audiences, we’re looking for a builder and connector who can create meaningful programs that inspire engagement, foster advocacy, and influence adoption. You’ll own flagship initiatives like hackathons, community recognition, and advocacy programs, while helping steward our community spaces. This is a high-impact role with a blend of strategic planning and hands-on execution, designed for someone who thrives at the intersection of operations, creativity, and community growth. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time role that can be held from one of our US hubs or remotely in the United States. &lt;/p&gt;
