&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and lead hackathon and contest programs that drive product adoption and community engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and scale an advocacy program to empower and enable passionate users to champion Figma&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop recognition and awards programs that spotlight community contributions and celebrate innovation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with product marketing, developer marketing, brand, events, and the broader community team to integrate community programs into key launches and moments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define, track, and report success metrics across growth, retention, advocacy, and adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We’d love to hear from you if you have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in community engagement, marketing, or related fields&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience running community programs at scale (e.g., hackathons, awards, ambassador/advocacy programs)&lt;/li&gt;
