&lt;li&gt;Excellent cross-functional collaboration skills with marketing, product, events, and brand teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Figma (bonus if you’re already part of our community)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strategic mentality with a hands-on approach; you’re comfortable switching between high-level planning and detailed execution&lt;/li&gt;
